/*This is to show the example of using case when statement during join in sql*/
/*======================================================================================
From Table 1 mbr
inner join Table2 pc
on 
mbr.firstvar=pc.pcvar
and 
mbr.emp_id=(case when pc.ph_id='TYC' then 'HYG' else pc.ph_id end)
and 
mbr.twovar=pc.flag
==========================================================================================*/
